column3: She'll make your pulse race while freezing your blood! The voluptuous Vamp Fatale!
On waves and flames they ride. The deadly duo─the Xtremes!
The match is decided! Victory goes to the challenger!
Ruling over all with an iron fist, the grand champion of the Arcadion─the Tyrant!
The match is decided! Before your very eyes, a new grand champion is born!
It's the shocking true face of the villainous president! The mighty serpent of yore─the Lindwurm!
Unbelievable─the champion's done it! The president has been defeated!
